                "imgDesc": "<p>This device was the result of early forays into optical science by the Institute of Natural Philosophy while they were still a budding academic organization. Its basic components include <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">\"beam generators\"</span> and <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">\"beam receivers.\"</span></p><p>The beam generator must sometimes be installed on a \"beam receiver\" base similar to a regulating valve, and can be controlled and rotated through the use of energy from a Xenochromatic Ball Octopus.</p>",
